signatureAbility.signatureDescription: Defenders with this ability can apply pressure to the quarterback from a greater distance.
Defenders with this ability use faster run shed moves for a better chance at shedding blocks against inside run plays.
Defenders with this ability will repair the fatigue of all defensive linemen on any 3rd or 4th down
Blockers with this ability reduce an edge pass rusher's chances of using a quick block shed move
Blockers with this ability are almost guaranteed to win any double team block they are engaged in
Players with this ability can detect user-controlled defenders before the snap; as well as 3rd and 4th down blitzers. Can be bluffed.
Players with this ability have a chance to replenish their stamina, once per play, when it is half depleted
Ballcarriers with this ability have steerable juke animations.
Receivers with this ability catch more consistently while catching passes 10-20 yards from the LoS, inside the numbers
Aggressive receivers overpower defenders and attack the football. When they enter the zone, this ability increases their success rate on aggressive catches against single coverage.
After securing a RAC catch, ballcarriers with this ability can quickly shift momentum, change direction, and turn the corner without sacrificing speed.
Receivers with this ability have a high success rate when creating separation on the last cut of any route.
Receivers with this ability catch more consistently while catching passes less than 10 yards from the LoS, inside the numbers
Receivers with this ability catch more consistently while catching passes 20+ yards from the LoS, outside the numbers
Ballcarriers with this ability will frequently attempt to gain extra yards while being tackled
Ballcarriers with this ability have steerable juke animations.
Defenders with this ability will frequently attempt and win impact blocks against receivers, tight ends, and running backs.
Defenders with this ability are highly likely to force catch knockouts against running backs.
The game's top defenders excel in all situations. When they enter the zone, this ability increases their chance of defeating run blocks, and disrupting catches via tackles.
Defenders with this ability can still tackle effectively while trying to strip the football.
Defenders with this ability have a greater chance of forcing fumbles when landing Perfect Hit Sticks
